{"tid":916971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國日常】蛇蠍美人虐殺動物自拍賣片　明碼實價屢禁不止","createTime":"2018-11-26T05:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T07:16:08.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"186fc53ca9f7258a01d412b23a5b61f2baa471b2","tid":916971,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181126/photo/bkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181126124657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181126124657&h=1d3f729c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">內地網絡有不少美女虐殺動物影片出售，且公然待價而沽。</span><br />\n<br />\n內地網絡近年出現不少虐殺動物的影片，惟此種歪風近來變本加厲，不但屢禁不止，且公然待價而沽，每片以數十元到數萬元（人民幣‧下同）不等的價錢出售。一些美女會在片中冷血虐殺兔子、貓狗等小動物，內容血腥；又會應購片者要求，「度身訂造」虐殺內容，令人髮指。部分美女更明碼實價在網上直播虐畜，引來各界關注。<br />\n<br />\n據內媒統計，僅是一名女主播，近幾年便曾拍攝162部視頻，當中曾涉嫌虐殺4隻小鳥、8隻小貓、33隻兔子、58隻小狗，以及幾十隻倉鼠和小雞。一名名叫阿佳的美女更聲稱「可訂製虐殺視頻，包括收取500元（約570港元）以高跟鞋踩死烏龜、牛蛙等小型動物；若付1.5萬元（約1.72萬港元），更會以閹割、剝皮等方法虐殺驢、羊等較大型動物。<br />\n<br />\n負責出售影片的周平表示：「只要敢踩，錢是分分鐘的事，拍得好不愁沒單子，只要膽子大。」據調查，不少網絡平台均有虐殺影片出售，用家可利用充值虛擬幣，來購買此類影片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181126/photo/bkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_02b.jpg?20181126124657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20181126124657&h=a9c58e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">美女用高跟鞋踩死兔子。（互聯網）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181126/photo/bkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_03b.jpg?20181126124657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_03b.jpg%3F20181126124657&h=28e0eb36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">美女在片中冷血虐殺兔子、貓狗和羊等動物，內容血腥。（互聯網）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181126/photo/bkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_04b.jpg?20181126124657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_04b.jpg%3F20181126124657&h=19f8dc41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">片中的美女均穿上高跟鞋來虐待動物。（互聯網）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181126/photo/bkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_05b.jpg?20181126124657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_05b.jpg%3F20181126124657&h=98ddb966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">美女先用毛巾覆蓋兔子，後者遭殘忍坐死。（互聯網）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181126/photo/bkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_06b.jpg?20181126124657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001_06b.jpg%3F20181126124657&h=c0c3104e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">美女會應購片者要求，「度身訂造」虐殺內容，令人髮指。（互聯網）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181126/bkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181126%2Fbkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001.html&d=ZCMZWLH%2B4d91uphMCSawOHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d4d93f43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181126/bkn-20181126114517791-1126_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e1b47f24d846715eeea1ccb340b5eb3f8396a735","tid":916971,"uid":204700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fda